uk.co.strangeskies.eclipse

Class EclipseModularTreeController

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.co.strangeskies.eclipse.EclipseModularTreeController

  • public class EclipseModularTreeController
extends Object
    A controller over a modular tree view for use within an Eclipse RCP environment.

    This class allows tree contributions to be contributed via contributors so that the contributions are instantiated according to an Eclipse injection context.
